{
  "video_id": "LhszKevcH30",
  "title": "How record collectors find lost music and preserve our cultural heritage | Alexis Charpentier",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12840.0,
      "end_time": 15760.0,
      "text": "I became obsessed with records when I was about 12 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16400.0,
      "end_time": 18576.0,
      "text": "My parents used to give me money to eat"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18600.0,
      "end_time": 20336.0,
      "text": "and on most days, instead of eating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20360.0,
      "end_time": 23736.0,
      "text": "I would save it and buy myself a record at the end of the week."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23760.0,
      "end_time": 26816.0,
      "text": "Here I am with a gigantic Walkman that&#39;s about half my leg --"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26840.0,
      "end_time": 28696.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28720.0,
      "end_time": 30576.0,
      "text": "It actually looks more like a VCR."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30600.0,
      "end_time": 32456.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32479.0,
      "end_time": 33736.0,
      "text": "So when I was a teenager,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 33760.0,
      "end_time": 37736.0,
      "text": "the obsession of buying cassettes, vinyls and CDs just kept growing."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37760.0,
      "end_time": 40736.0,
      "text": "I was even working in a record store for many years"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40760.0,
      "end_time": 42600.0,
      "text": "and only ever got paid in records."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43680.0,
      "end_time": 46456.0,
      "text": "One day I realized that I had thousands of records more"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46480.0,
      "end_time": 49560.0,
      "text": "than I could even listen to in my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49800.0,
      "end_time": 51560.0,
      "text": "I became what many of us are:"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51800.0,
      "end_time": 52856.0,
      "text": "record junkies --"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 52880.0,
      "end_time": 55680.0,
      "text": "or record diggers, as we like to call ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 56480.0,
      "end_time": 58535.0,
      "text": "Record digging, as the name suggests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 58560.0,
      "end_time": 60696.0,
      "text": "means getting your hands dirty."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 60720.0,
      "end_time": 64256.0,
      "text": "It means spending hours rummaging through warehouses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 64280.0,
      "end_time": 65536.0,
      "text": "church basements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 65560.0,
      "end_time": 67816.0,
      "text": "yard sales, record stores --"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 67840.0,
      "end_time": 71336.0,
      "text": "all to find records that have been forgotten for decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 71360.0,
      "end_time": 73480.0,
      "text": "Records that have become cultural waste."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 74280.0,
      "end_time": 78496.0,
      "text": "The earliest record collectors from about the &#39;30s to the 1960s"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 78520.0,
      "end_time": 81336.0,
      "text": "found and preserved so many important records"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 81360.0,
      "end_time": 83400.0,
      "text": "that would have been lost forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 84280.0,
      "end_time": 87216.0,
      "text": "In those days, most cultural and public institutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 87240.0,
      "end_time": 89455.0,
      "text": "didn&#39;t really care to preserve these treasures."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 89480.0,
      "end_time": 92360.0,
      "text": "In many cases, they were just throwing them into the garbage."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 93680.0,
      "end_time": 95616.0,
      "text": "Record digging is a lifestyle."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 95640.0,
      "end_time": 99560.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re absolutely obsessed with obscure records,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 99800.0,
      "end_time": 101256.0,
      "text": "expensive records, dollar-bin records,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 101280.0,
      "end_time": 102576.0,
      "text": "crazy artwork,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 102600.0,
      "end_time": 103960.0,
      "text": "sub-subgenres."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 104680.0,
      "end_time": 108456.0,
      "text": "And all of the tiniest details that go with each release."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 108480.0,
      "end_time": 110576.0,
      "text": "When the media talks about the vinyl revival"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 110600.0,
      "end_time": 112655.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s been happening these last few years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 112680.0,
      "end_time": 115576.0,
      "text": "they often forget to mention this community"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 115600.0,
      "end_time": 120336.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s been keeping the vinyl and the tradition and the culture alive"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 120360.0,
      "end_time": 121960.0,
      "text": "for these last 30 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 122800.0,
      "end_time": 126136.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a very close-knit but competitive society, a little bit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 126160.0,
      "end_time": 129216.0,
      "text": "because when you&#39;re hunting for extremely rare records,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 129240.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130656.00000000001,
      "text": "if you miss your opportunity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 130680.0,
      "end_time": 132920.0,
      "text": "you might not see that record ever in your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 134400.0,
      "end_time": 138816.0,
      "text": "But I guess the only person in here truly impressed by record collectors"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 138840.0,
      "end_time": 140360.0,
      "text": "is another record collector."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 141680.0,
      "end_time": 142936.0,
      "text": "To the outside world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 142960.0,
      "end_time": 147160.0,
      "text": "we seem like a very weird, oddball group of individuals."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 147400.0,
      "end_time": 148256.0,
      "text": "And --"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 148280.0,
      "end_time": 149696.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 149720.0,
      "end_time": 150936.0,
      "text": "And they&#39;re mostly right."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 150960.0,
      "end_time": 153616.0,
      "text": "All the record collectors I know are obsessive maniacs."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 153640.0,
      "end_time": 155679.0,
      "text": "We know we&#39;re all crazy in some way."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 156320.0,
      "end_time": 159256.0,
      "text": "But I think we should be viewed a little bit more like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 159280.0,
      "end_time": 160296.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 160320.0,
      "end_time": 161656.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re music archaeologists."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 161680.0,
      "end_time": 163880.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re hunting down the lost artifact."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 164320.0,
      "end_time": 167936.0,
      "text": "We all have a list of records that we would do anything to get our hands on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 167960.0,
      "end_time": 169616.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;ve been chasing for years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 169640.0,
      "end_time": 171959.0,
      "text": "and we actually call this list our \"holy grails.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 173200.0,
      "end_time": 174816.0,
      "text": "When you&#39;re digging for records,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 174840.0,
      "end_time": 176976.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re surrounded by music you don&#39;t know."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 177000.0,
      "end_time": 180296.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re surrounded by mystery and by all these dreams --"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 180320.0,
      "end_time": 182280.0,
      "text": "records that people once believed in."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 183200.0,
      "end_time": 186736.0,
      "text": "Imagine the thousands of artists who were destined to be legends"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 186760.0,
      "end_time": 190376.0,
      "text": "but for various reasons, were just overlooked."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 190400.0,
      "end_time": 193616.0,
      "text": "Many of these records only exist in a handful of copies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 193640.0,
      "end_time": 195896.0,
      "text": "and some have never even been found,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 195920.0,
      "end_time": 197136.0,
      "text": "never been heard."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 197160.0,
      "end_time": 199240.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re literally endangered species."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 200480.0,
      "end_time": 201736.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll tell you a story"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 201760.0,
      "end_time": 206696.0,
      "text": "that for me sort of sums up the value of the work of record diggers."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 206720.0,
      "end_time": 209760.0,
      "text": "The story of a brilliant Montreal musician and composer."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 211600.0,
      "end_time": 214536.0,
      "text": "Henri-Pierre Noël was born and raised in Haiti,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 214560.0,
      "end_time": 217800.0,
      "text": "but he lived briefly in the US and in Belgium."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 217760.0,
      "end_time": 220856.0,
      "text": "He passed through Montreal what was supposed to be for two weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 220880.0,
      "end_time": 223550.0,
      "text": "but he ended up staying for the next 40 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 223800.0,
      "end_time": 225136.0,
      "text": "When he was young, he learned to play piano"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 225160.0,
      "end_time": 228960.0,
      "text": "and developed a very particular way of playing his instrument:"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 228120.0,
      "end_time": 230000.0,
      "text": "very fast and almost like a percussion."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 230960.0,
      "end_time": 235560.0,
      "text": "His style was a mix of his Haitian influences and folklore"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 235800.0,
      "end_time": 238616.0,
      "text": "mixed with the American influences that he grew up hearing."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 238640.0,
      "end_time": 242799.0,
      "text": "So he created a mix of compas mixed with funk and jazz."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 243800.0,
      "end_time": 245160.0,
      "text": "As a young man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 245400.0,
      "end_time": 247935.0,
      "text": "he played and toured with live bands in the US and in Europe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 247960.0,
      "end_time": 251320.0,
      "text": "but had never recorded an album or a song before moving to Canada."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 252200.0,
      "end_time": 254655.0,
      "text": "It was in Montreal in 1979"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 254680.0,
      "end_time": 257296.0,
      "text": "that he released his first album called, \"Piano.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 257320.0,
      "end_time": 260320.0,
      "text": "Completely on his own, on Henri-Pierre Noël Records."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 261399.99999999997,
      "end_time": 264320.0,
      "text": "He only made what he could afford: 2,000 copies of the record."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 265520.0,
      "end_time": 267840.0,
      "text": "The record received a little bit of airplay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 268519.0,
      "end_time": 271495.0,
      "text": "a little bit of support in Canada and in Haiti,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 271519.0,
      "end_time": 273976.0,
      "text": "but without a big label behind it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 274000.0,
      "end_time": 275600.0,
      "text": "it was very, very difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 276400.0,
      "end_time": 277616.0,
      "text": "Back then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 277640.0,
      "end_time": 280336.0,
      "text": "if your record wasn&#39;t getting played on mainstream radio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 280360.0,
      "end_time": 283576.0,
      "text": "if you weren&#39;t in jukeboxes or if you weren&#39;t invited to play on TV,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 283600.0,
      "end_time": 285416.0,
      "text": "the odds were completely against you."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 285440.0,
      "end_time": 288560.0,
      "text": "Releasing an album as an independent artist"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 288800.0,
      "end_time": 290176.0,
      "text": "was so much more difficult than it is today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 290200.0,
      "end_time": 293816.0,
      "text": "both in terms of being heard and just distributing the thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 293840.0,
      "end_time": 297150.0,
      "text": "So, soon after, he released a second album,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 297400.0,
      "end_time": 300960.0,
      "text": "kept a busy schedule playing piano in various clubs in the city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 300120.0,
      "end_time": 303280.0,
      "text": "but his records started to accumulate dust slowly."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 304400.0,
      "end_time": 306816.0,
      "text": "And those 2,000 copies in the span of 30 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 306840.0,
      "end_time": 308816.0,
      "text": "easily started to get lost"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 308840.0,
      "end_time": 312000.0,
      "text": "until only a few copies in the world remained."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 312840.0,
      "end_time": 315215.0,
      "text": "Then in the mid-2000s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 315240.0,
      "end_time": 318960.0,
      "text": "a Montreal record digger that goes by the name Kobal"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 318120.0,
      "end_time": 321240.0,
      "text": "was doing his weekly rounds of just hunting for records."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 321720.0,
      "end_time": 323376.0,
      "text": "He was in a flea market"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 323400.0,
      "end_time": 327496.0,
      "text": "surrounded by thousands of other dirty, dusty, moldy records."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 327520.0,
      "end_time": 329440.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s where he found the \"Piano\" album."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 330600.0,
      "end_time": 332456.0,
      "text": "He wasn&#39;t specifically looking for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 332480.0,
      "end_time": 334816.0,
      "text": "Actually, you could say it sort of found him."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 334840.0,
      "end_time": 338816.0,
      "text": "You could also say that after 20 years of record digging every single week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 338840.0,
      "end_time": 341400.0,
      "text": "he had developed a sixth sense for finding the gold."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 342840.0,
      "end_time": 344816.0,
      "text": "He took the record and inspected it:"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 344840.0,
      "end_time": 347655.0,
      "text": "the front, the artwork, the back, the liner notes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 347680.0,
      "end_time": 351376.0,
      "text": "and he was intrigued by the fact that this Haitian musician made a record"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 351400.0,
      "end_time": 353736.0,
      "text": "in Quebec in the late &#39;70s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 353760.0,
      "end_time": 355599.0,
      "text": "so he was intrigued."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 356240.0,
      "end_time": 358816.0,
      "text": "He took out his little, plastic, portable turntable"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 358840.0,
      "end_time": 362695.0,
      "text": "that he brought with him whenever he was on these digging quests"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 362720.0,
      "end_time": 364376.0,
      "text": "and put the record on."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 364400.0,
      "end_time": 366390.0,
      "text": "So why don&#39;t we do the same thing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 374640.0,
      "end_time": 378000.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 405680.0,
      "end_time": 409736.0,
      "text": "He fell in love with the music instantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 409760.0,
      "end_time": 411816.0,
      "text": "but he had to know the backstory behind it."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 411840.0,
      "end_time": 413560.0,
      "text": "He didn&#39;t know where it came from."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 414760.0,
      "end_time": 416150.0,
      "text": "He knew the artist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 416400.0,
      "end_time": 417456.0,
      "text": "at the time of the recording,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 417480.0,
      "end_time": 418736.0,
      "text": "was living in Montreal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 418760.0,
      "end_time": 420760.0,
      "text": "so for months, he tried to track him down."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 421520.0,
      "end_time": 425120.0,
      "text": "He even found Noël&#39;s business card inside the record sleeve."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 425640.0,
      "end_time": 429159.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s how DIY Henri-Pierre Noël was."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 429680.0,
      "end_time": 433176.0,
      "text": "So he found the card inside the record sleeve --"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 433200.0,
      "end_time": 434616.0,
      "text": "of course he did try to call,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 434640.0,
      "end_time": 437390.0,
      "text": "but after 30 years, the number didn&#39;t work anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 438880.0,
      "end_time": 440936.0,
      "text": "So it was only in Belgium,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 440960.0,
      "end_time": 442536.0,
      "text": "where the artist had once lived,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 442560.0,
      "end_time": 445696.0,
      "text": "that Kobal managed to find someone that knew the artist personally"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 445720.0,
      "end_time": 447400.0,
      "text": "and gave him the contact."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 447520.0,
      "end_time": 450575.0,
      "text": "So when he finally sat down with the artist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 450600.0,
      "end_time": 455800.0,
      "text": "he made him a promise to someday find a way to get the album rereleased."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 457200.0,
      "end_time": 460816.0,
      "text": "He then arranged for a British label called Wah Wah 45s"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 460840.0,
      "end_time": 462719.0,
      "text": "to get the two albums reissued."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 463680.0,
      "end_time": 465496.0,
      "text": "And what happens very often is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 465520.0,
      "end_time": 466775.0,
      "text": "in these reissue projects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 466800.0,
      "end_time": 469936.0,
      "text": "that it becomes very difficult to find the master tapes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 469960.0,
      "end_time": 472560.0,
      "text": "the original recording of the sessions."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 472800.0,
      "end_time": 475560.0,
      "text": "Art can be destroyed by fires, floods, earthquakes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 475800.0,
      "end_time": 476296.0,
      "text": "thrown in the garbage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 476320.0,
      "end_time": 477816.0,
      "text": "or just lost forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 477840.0,
      "end_time": 479560.0,
      "text": "But thankfully,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 479800.0,
      "end_time": 480895.0,
      "text": "the Henri-Pierre Noël tapes were safe"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 480920.0,
      "end_time": 482640.0,
      "text": "and they were ready for remastering."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 483320.0,
      "end_time": 485296.0,
      "text": "The record was finally rereleased"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 485320.0,
      "end_time": 489320.0,
      "text": "and received praise from music critics, DJs and listeners worldwide --"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 490800.0,
      "end_time": 493200.0,
      "text": "the praise that it should have received in 1979."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 495360.0,
      "end_time": 498816.0,
      "text": "The artist was so inspired that he decided to revive his music career,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 498840.0,
      "end_time": 501599.0,
      "text": "get back on a stage, and play for new audiences."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 502680.0,
      "end_time": 505456.0,
      "text": "The artist, now in his 60s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 505480.0,
      "end_time": 507776.0,
      "text": "told me, \"This changed everything for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 507800.0,
      "end_time": 509456.0,
      "text": "I went from planning my retirement"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 509480.0,
      "end_time": 513800.0,
      "text": "to playing on the BBC Radio in London, and on Radio Canada and more.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 513760.0,
      "end_time": 515576.0,
      "text": "But also it gave him a chance to play"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 515600.0,
      "end_time": 518960.0,
      "text": "in front of his three sons for the first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 518120.0,
      "end_time": 523176.0,
      "text": "To me, this story shows perfectly the work of record diggers at its best."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 523200.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525176.0,
      "text": "Beyond the rarity and the dollar value --"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 525200.0,
      "end_time": 528135.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ll be honest, we&#39;re totally obsessed by that --"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 528159.0,
      "end_time": 531616.0,
      "text": "the true beauty is to give art a second chance;"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 531640.0,
      "end_time": 533240.0,
      "text": "to save art from oblivion."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 534480.0,
      "end_time": 537776.0,
      "text": "The work of a good record digger is a constant loop of three phases."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 537800.0,
      "end_time": 539439.0,
      "text": "The first thing we do is hunt."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 540400.0,
      "end_time": 542136.0,
      "text": "We spend hours, days, years of our lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 542160.0,
      "end_time": 545216.0,
      "text": "rummaging through dirty and dusty record bins."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 545240.0,
      "end_time": 548360.0,
      "text": "Everything that we can do to find our hands on the gold."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 550000.0,
      "end_time": 552256.0,
      "text": "Yes, you can find good records online,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 552280.0,
      "end_time": 553736.0,
      "text": "but for the deepest treasures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 553760.0,
      "end_time": 556000.0,
      "text": "you need to get off the couch and into the wild."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 556400.0,
      "end_time": 559295.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why we call it record digging and not record clicking."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 559320.0,
      "end_time": 560456.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 560480.0,
      "end_time": 562680.0,
      "text": "So what we are is music archaeologists."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 563240.0,
      "end_time": 565416.0,
      "text": "But then the next thing we do is we gather."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 565440.0,
      "end_time": 567696.0,
      "text": "Based on our taste, expertise, personal agenda,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 567720.0,
      "end_time": 570560.0,
      "text": "we choose carefully which records to save,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 570800.0,
      "end_time": 572256.0,
      "text": "which records mean something to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 572280.0,
      "end_time": 575935.0,
      "text": "We then try and find out every little thing we can about that record --"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 575960.0,
      "end_time": 577416.0,
      "text": "the artist, the label"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 577440.0,
      "end_time": 579456.0,
      "text": "and supervital information"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 579480.0,
      "end_time": 582000.0,
      "text": "like \"Who&#39;s that playing trumpet on track three?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 582960.0,
      "end_time": 584936.0,
      "text": "Then we file them, we contextualize them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 584960.0,
      "end_time": 586216.0,
      "text": "and we keep them safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 586240.0,
      "end_time": 587720.0,
      "text": "We are music archivists."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 588400.0,
      "end_time": 591136.0,
      "text": "And the last thing we do to close the loop is we share."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 591160.0,
      "end_time": 594815.0,
      "text": "Most record diggers that I know have some sort of a way"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 594840.0,
      "end_time": 597256.0,
      "text": "to share their discovery and elevate the artist"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 597280.0,
      "end_time": 598536.0,
      "text": "through an album reissue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 598560.0,
      "end_time": 600880.0,
      "text": "a web article, a radio show."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 601800.0,
      "end_time": 604880.0,
      "text": "We give records back their rightful place in music history."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 605520.0,
      "end_time": 607960.0,
      "text": "We are tastemakers and curators."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 607120.0,
      "end_time": 608400.0,
      "text": "We are musicologists."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 609720.0,
      "end_time": 610936.0,
      "text": "So for myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 610960.0,
      "end_time": 613936.0,
      "text": "and most of the record collectors I&#39;ve encountered in 20 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 613960.0,
      "end_time": 616376.0,
      "text": "I think that we all have some sort of an outlet"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 616400.0,
      "end_time": 617656.0,
      "text": "for these discoveries."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 617680.0,
      "end_time": 621736.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s our way to keep our sanity and sort of sense of purpose"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 621760.0,
      "end_time": 624536.0,
      "text": "in this very maddening obsession,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 624560.0,
      "end_time": 626455.0,
      "text": "because it can be sort of a lonely one."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 626480.0,
      "end_time": 629195.0,
      "text": "But I think we also do it because it serves the human need"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 629219.0,
      "end_time": 630819.0,
      "text": "to pass along cultural knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 631920.0,
      "end_time": 634960.0,
      "text": "Speaking of the need for curation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 634120.0,
      "end_time": 636160.0,
      "text": "in an era of overwhelming choice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 636400.0,
      "end_time": 637295.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s been demonstrated"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 637320.0,
      "end_time": 639936.0,
      "text": "that too much choice actually hinders discovery."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 639960.0,
      "end_time": 641176.0,
      "text": "For example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 641200.0,
      "end_time": 643816.0,
      "text": "if you&#39;re trying to watch something on Netflix,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 643840.0,
      "end_time": 648336.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re actually only browsing through a catalog of 6,000 titles."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 648360.0,
      "end_time": 650256.0,
      "text": "Now, compare that with Spotify;"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 650280.0,
      "end_time": 652376.0,
      "text": "if you want to pick something to listen to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 652400.0,
      "end_time": 656136.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re browsing through a catalog of 30 million songs."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 656160.0,
      "end_time": 657415.0,
      "text": "So I think as you can see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 657440.0,
      "end_time": 659616.0,
      "text": "this notion of paralysis by choice"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 659640.0,
      "end_time": 662696.0,
      "text": "affects music more than movies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 662720.0,
      "end_time": 664136.0,
      "text": "for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 664160.0,
      "end_time": 665415.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s a few studies"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 665440.0,
      "end_time": 667616.0,
      "text": "that are starting to show the effects of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 667640.0,
      "end_time": 669376.0,
      "text": "A recent look at the UK music market"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 669400.0,
      "end_time": 674816.0,
      "text": "shows that the top one percent of artists in the UK are actually earning 77 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 674840.0,
      "end_time": 677456.0,
      "text": "of the total revenues inside the music industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 677480.0,
      "end_time": 678976.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s 2013,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 679000.0,
      "end_time": 682216.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s progressively getting worse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 682240.0,
      "end_time": 684160.0,
      "text": "or progressing."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 684400.0,
      "end_time": 686896.0,
      "text": "Anyway, if you&#39;re in the one percent, I&#39;m sure you&#39;re happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 686920.0,
      "end_time": 688175.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 688200.0,
      "end_time": 690560.0,
      "text": "So the takeaway for me is"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 691640.0,
      "end_time": 695680.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s easier for people to listen to music than ever before."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 696960.0,
      "end_time": 699696.0,
      "text": "People have more music at their disposal than ever before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 699720.0,
      "end_time": 703496.0,
      "text": "yet people choose to listen to more of the same music than ever before."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 703520.0,
      "end_time": 704760.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s a sad thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 707760.0,
      "end_time": 711896.0,
      "text": "Inspired by my love for music research, record digging and curation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 711920.0,
      "end_time": 716550.0,
      "text": "I started a website called \"Music Is My Sanctuary\" in 2007."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 716800.0,
      "end_time": 719816.0,
      "text": "Our slogan has always been \"Future Classics and Forgotten Treasures.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 719840.0,
      "end_time": 722336.0,
      "text": "And it shows our love for discovering music"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 722360.0,
      "end_time": 724936.0,
      "text": "and introducing music both old and new."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 724960.0,
      "end_time": 726216.0,
      "text": "From humble beginnings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 726240.0,
      "end_time": 729560.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve built a worldwide platform with a massive audience"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 729800.0,
      "end_time": 731256.0,
      "text": "with over 100 collaborators."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 731280.0,
      "end_time": 733616.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve created over 10,000 pieces of content,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 733640.0,
      "end_time": 736000.0,
      "text": "over 500 hours of audio content."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 736880.0,
      "end_time": 738376.0,
      "text": "Our audience consists of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 738400.0,
      "end_time": 740856.0,
      "text": "who just want more than what&#39;s being offered to them"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 740880.0,
      "end_time": 742376.0,
      "text": "by mainstream music channels."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 742400.0,
      "end_time": 743600.0,
      "text": "They want to do --"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 744320.0,
      "end_time": 745656.0,
      "text": "they want to dig deeper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 745680.0,
      "end_time": 749599.0,
      "text": "but they don&#39;t necessarily have 20 hours a week like us nerds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 750440.0,
      "end_time": 752240.0,
      "text": "so they trust us to do that for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 753400.0,
      "end_time": 755536.0,
      "text": "Curation is at the heart of everything we do."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 755560.0,
      "end_time": 758119.0,
      "text": "We believe in human recommendations over algorithms."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 760680.0,
      "end_time": 764335.0,
      "text": "I could talk about the passion of record digging for days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 764360.0,
      "end_time": 766576.0,
      "text": "but let me conclude this way."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 766600.0,
      "end_time": 768336.0,
      "text": "After many years of doing it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 768360.0,
      "end_time": 773160.0,
      "text": "a record collector&#39;s collection becomes sort of his autobiography."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 774880.0,
      "end_time": 777136.0,
      "text": "Last year, I was DJ-ing in Poland,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 777160.0,
      "end_time": 779136.0,
      "text": "and the people that were hosting me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 779160.0,
      "end_time": 781256.0,
      "text": "they had this amazing record collection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 781280.0,
      "end_time": 782896.0,
      "text": "and of course I was intrigued"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 782920.0,
      "end_time": 785496.0,
      "text": "and I said, \"Are you selling these?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 785520.0,
      "end_time": 788960.0,
      "text": "They then explained to me that it was the collection"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 788120.0,
      "end_time": 793000.0,
      "text": "that belonged to their dear friend Maceo who passed away a few months earlier."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 793600.0,
      "end_time": 797176.0,
      "text": "And they were doing a project of inviting different people"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 797200.0,
      "end_time": 800960.0,
      "text": "to take the collection and to create something new from it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 800120.0,
      "end_time": 802576.0,
      "text": "whether it&#39;s sampling or DJ mixes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 802600.0,
      "end_time": 804776.0,
      "text": "you know, just to give it a second life."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 804800.0,
      "end_time": 807776.0,
      "text": "And so after a few hours of going through the collection myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 807800.0,
      "end_time": 809976.0,
      "text": "and creating a DJ mix from it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 810000.0,
      "end_time": 812456.0,
      "text": "even though I never got the chance to meet him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 812480.0,
      "end_time": 815960.0,
      "text": "it felt like in a special way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 815120.0,
      "end_time": 816336.0,
      "text": "me and him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 816360.0,
      "end_time": 818480.0,
      "text": "we got to talk about records for a few hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 819120.0,
      "end_time": 821800.0,
      "text": "So, as record diggers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 822760.0,
      "end_time": 825856.0,
      "text": "our work and our record collections are there"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 825880.0,
      "end_time": 827760.0,
      "text": "to be passed on to the next generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 828360.0,
      "end_time": 831480.0,
      "text": "Beautiful art deserves to be cherished, shared and rediscovered."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 834120.0,
      "end_time": 835816.0,
      "text": "Embrace curators;"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 835840.0,
      "end_time": 839160.0,
      "text": "we are alternative voices to the mainstream music channels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 839400.0,
      "end_time": 840400.0,
      "text": "digital or otherwise."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 841240.0,
      "end_time": 842720.0,
      "text": "Go beyond the algorithm."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 843920.0,
      "end_time": 845496.0,
      "text": "Whatever kind of music you like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 845520.0,
      "end_time": 849896.0,
      "text": "there are so many websites, radio shows, DJs, record stores out there"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 849920.0,
      "end_time": 852656.0,
      "text": "that are just waiting to share their discoveries with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 852680.0,
      "end_time": 854160.0,
      "text": "We do this work for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 854400.0,
      "end_time": 857550.0,
      "text": "All you have to do is open your ears and take risks."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 857800.0,
      "end_time": 859160.0,
      "text": "This music will change your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 859400.0,
      "end_time": 860256.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 860280.0,
      "end_time": 864280.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}